p spectra expected of pulsars. Furthermore, the flux\ndistribution of the sources agrees well with the standard pulsar luminosity\nfunction. The total luminosity and number of objects observed suggest that\nTerzan 5 contains more pulsars than any other Galactic globular cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 1999 22:12:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
